text:
Finally was able to come back and finish watching the rest of this stream.  The DRG brain rot is real. Hope you girls get the perms quick.  Also, hearing you talk about The Hobbit movies just made me feel so vindicated.  I love the books, I own multiple copies and have read them several times over the years, but I HATED those movies.  I'm not sure I even went to see the third in theaters.  I went to see the first with my sister on my birthday, the first time we had gotten to do something together in ages and I just couldn't sit still because everything bugged me.  I think eventually I watched some unofficial cut of the movie that removed parts to better follow the book and it was more tolerable. 

Anyways, thanks for more palworld, hope to see you on with some others again, I think playing with IRyS would be a lot of fun, but she does stream very late for you.  She might like DRG too.

Take care, I'll see you on your next stream.
